[SN]TITLE[SN]
Philippe Senderos: Ex-Aston Villa defender joins Grasshoppers

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Former Arsenal and Aston Villa defender Philippe Senderos has joined Grasshoppers Zurich in Switzerland.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The 30-year-old was a free agent after agreeing with Aston Villa this week to terminate his contract following 18 months in the West Midlands.
Senderos, who also played for Fulham and had a loan spell at Everton, has signed a six-month contract.
The Switzerland international has played at three World Cups and hopes to feature at Euro 2016 in France.
